      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RELAX MATE (1) has a terrific record this track and trip with two wins and four placings from six starts. Comes off a (21.81) win last time, scoring by 5.5 lengths in a Mix 6/7 over 390m at this track. Looks well placed and should feature. HYLAND AZULA (2) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at her last four runs. Last time finished 3rd in a Grade 5 on March 23 over 390m at this track behind Paw Elodee beaten 7 lengths (22.50). Winning chance. SCOTT CHARISMA (7) broke a string of placings finishing in the money four on end before a last start fifth (22.53) at this track. Form here sound including four wins. Cannot be taken lightly. THERMAL FLAME (3) has top-three claims while fresh from a five-and-a-half weeks break.",
